&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Context of the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a high energy, &quot;hands on&quot; Director of Demand Generation to serve as the chief architect of Thunes’ global revenue engine. This is a critical leadership role for a &quot;doer&quot; who thrives in a high growth environment and is passionate about building a sophisticated, tech enabled demand generation machine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will bridge the gap between marketing strategy, digital execution, and sales performance. You will own the entire lifecycle of a lead from initial digital acquisition and automated nurturing to the rigorous qualification of opportunities by your global SDR team. At Thunes, we navigate long sales cycles and a complex Account Based Marketing (ABM) strategy; your mission is to ensure quality, intent, and strategic alignment across our global target account lists to drive meaningful, scalable pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Demand Gen Team Composition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will lead and grow a multidisciplinary global team designed to support our 24/7 global network:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global SDR Team:&lt;/strong&gt; A high velocity squad based in the UK, Spain, Philippines, and the USA focused on both inbound qualification and strategic outbound prospecting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Digital Marketing:&lt;/strong&gt; Specialists managing our &quot;always on&quot; paid and organic channels, ensuring a constant flow of high intent traffic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marketing Operations:&lt;/strong&gt; A centralized function (based in Manila) dedicated to data integrity, lead scoring, tech stack integrations, and automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;External Partners:&lt;/strong&gt; Management of specialist agencies for Web Development, LinkedIn Ads, and SEO.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Demand Generation and Digital Strategy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End to End Demand Funnel:&lt;/strong&gt; Architect and manage the full funnel, including target account identification, lead acquisition, and automated multi touch nurture streams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Digital and Search Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversee global paid media (LinkedIn Ads) and organic growth. Future proof our visibility by optimizing for traditional SEO as well as emerging GEO (Generative Engine Optimization) and AEO (Answer Engine Optimization).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABM and Strategic Targeting:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead our Account Based Marketing efforts, leveraging intent data (6sense) to engage &quot;Gorilla&quot; and Tier 1 accounts with personalized journeys.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Omnichannel Campaigns:&lt;/strong&gt; Execute integrated campaigns across all channels, while supporting Field Marketing for localized in person events and content activation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SDR Leadership and Sales Alignment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global Team Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead, coach, and scale your global SDR team, standardizing &quot;playbooks&quot; for outbound excellence and ensuring rigorous qualification before handoff.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales and Enablement Alignment:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain a &quot;locked at the hip&quot; relationship with Sales Leadership, Account Management, and Sales Enablement to refine lead quality and feedback loops.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
