&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pre-Sales Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join our dynamic team as a Pre-Sales Engineer, where you will play a crucial role in bridging the gap between our sales, product, and onboarding teams. Your expertise will ensure that our merchant and pay-in partners are provided with tailored solutions that leverage Thunes&#39; innovative products, while also gaining insights into industry trends and competitor strategies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the sales team during the pre-sales and technical pre-sales cycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand the merchant and pay-in partners&#39; needs and propose suitable solutions using the company&#39;s product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather the partner&#39;s requirements, validate the use cases, and confirm the project scope before handing it over to the inbound onboarding team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform market research to become knowledgeable about our industry and competitors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be an expert on our different products at Thunes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 - 5 years of experience in solution consulting and technical project management with external stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of payment and merchant solutions in the fintech domain.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills with the ability to pitch Thunes, explain our product clearly, and translate needs/requirements to the product team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
